      <category>
        <pattern>COILS</pattern>
        <template>
          The cooling coil elements on the back of a fridge can get dirty. This reduces the efficiency of the fridge as it needs to work harder to produce the same amount of cooling. Cleaning the dirt and dust off the coils allows the fridge to work properly again.
        </template>
      </category>
      <category>
